<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
        <title>Kaoula</title>

        <!-- Bootstrap -->
        <link
            href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
            rel="stylesheet"
            integrity="sha384-gH2yIJqKdNHPEq0n4Mqa/HGKIhSkIHeL5AyhkYV8i59U5AR6csBvApHHNl/vI1Bx"
            crossorigin="anonymous"
        />
        <!-- Fontawesome -->
        <link
            rel="stylesheet"
            href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.1.2/css/all.min.css"
            integrity="sha512-1sCRPdkRXhBV2PBLUdRb4tMg1w2YPf37qatUFeS7zlBy7jJI8Lf4VHwWfZZfpXtYSLy85pkm9GaYVYMfw5BC1A=="
            crossorigin="anonymous"
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
        />
        <!-- Custom -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
    </head>
    <body>

        <%- include("./components/spinner.ejs") %> 

        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-light">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
                    <img
                        src="./kaoula.png"
                        alt="Kaoula Logo"
                        class="rounded-circle"
                        width="45"
                        height="45"
                    />
                </a>
                <button
                    class="navbar-toggler"
                    type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                    data-bs-target="#navbarSupportedContent"
                    aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent"
                    aria-expanded="false"
                    aria-label="Toggle navigation"
                >
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <div
                    class="collapse navbar-collapse"
                    id="navbarSupportedContent"
                >
                    <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0"></ul>
                    <div class="d-flex" role="login">
                        <% if (user) { %>

                        <div class="dropdown">
                            <button
                                class="btn btn-secondary dropdown-toggle"
                                type="button"
                                dropdown-toggle
                                data-bs-toggle="dropdown"
                                aria-expanded="false"
                            >
                                <img
                                    src="<%= user.avatar %>"
                                    alt="<%= user.name %>"
                                    class="rounded-circle"
                                    width="25"
                                    height="25"
                                />

                                <%= user.username %>
                            </button>
                            <div class="dropdown-menu">
                                <a class="dropdown-item" href="/profile">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-user-circle"></i>
                                    Mine oplysninger
                                </a>
                                <a class="dropdown-item" href="/classes">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-chalkboard-user"></i>
                                    Mine klasser
                                </a>

                                <% if (user.role == 5) { %>
                                <a class="dropdown-item" href="/classes/new">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-user-plus"></i>
                                    Lav en ny klasse
                                </a>
                                <% } %>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <a
                            class="btn btn-danger my-2 my-sm-0"
                            style="margin-left: 5px"
                            href="/auth/logout"
                        >
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-lock-open"></i> Log af
                        </a>

                        <% } else { %>
                        <a
                            class="btn btn-brand my-2 my-sm-0"
                            href="/auth/google"
                        >
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-lock"></i> Log på
                        </a>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <div class="px-4 pt-5 my-5 text-center border-bottom">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold"><%- config.home.site_name %></h1>
            <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
                <p class="lead mb-4"><%- config.home.site_description %></p>
                <div
                    class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center mb-5"
                >
                    <% if (user) { %>
                    <a
                        href="/classes"
                        class="btn btn-brand btn-lg px-4 me-sm-3"
                    >
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-chalkboard-user"></i> Mine klasser
                    </button>
                    <% } else { %>
                    <a href="/auth/google" class="btn btn-brand btn-lg px-4 me-sm-3">
                        <i class="fa-brands fa-google"></i> Log på med google
                    </a>
                    <% } %>

                    <a href="/about" class="btn btn-mid btn-lg px-4">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i> Lær mere
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="overflow-hidden" style="max-height: 30vh">
                <div class="container px-5">
                    <img
                        src="https://i.ibb.co/mc7zctM/kaula-example.png"
                        class="img-fluid border rounded-3 shadow-lg mb-4"
                        alt="Example image"
                        width="700"
                        height="500"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container col-xxl-8 px-4 py-5">
            <div class="row flex-lg-row-reverse align-items-center g-5 py-5">
              <div class="col-10 col-sm-8 col-lg-6">
                <img src="https://i.ibb.co/DzBpZ1R/settings-kaula.png" class="d-block mx-lg-auto img-fluid" alt="Settings" width="700" height="500" loading="lazy" style="border-radius:4px">
              </div>
              <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold lh-1 mb-3">Som lærer...</h1>
                <p class="lead">Når du er lærer kan du lave klasser og inviter dine elever. Du kan bla. give dem lektier for eller opgaver. Er du en lærer? Så ansøg i dag for at komme igang!</p>
                <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-start">
                  <button type="button" class="btn btn-brand btn-lg px-4 me-md-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i> Ansøg</button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container my-5">
            <div class="row p-4 pb-0 pe-lg-0 pt-lg-5 align-items-center rounded-3 border shadow-lg">
              <div class="col-lg-7 p-3 p-lg-5 pt-lg-3">
                <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold lh-1">Selv hosting...</h1>
                <p class="lead">Mangler du din egen skole portal, som du har 100% selv kontrol over? Læs vores guide til at host din egen Kaoula på ingen tid.</p>
                <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-start mb-4 mb-lg-3">
                  <a href="/guide" class="btn btn-mid btn-lg px-4 me-md-2 fw-bold"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i> Kom igang</a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-lg-4 offset-lg-1 p-0 overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
                  <img class="rounded-lg-3" src="https://i.ibb.co/TR5sSLp/userdasuhboard.png" alt="" width="720">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        <%- include("./footer.ejs") %>

        <!-- Scripts -->
        <script
            src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-A3rJD856KowSb7dwlZdYEkO39Gagi7vIsF0jrRAoQmDKKtQBHUuLZ9AsSv4jD4Xa"
            crossorigin="anonymous"
        ></script>
    </body>
</html>
